=== Asia-Pacific ===

The phone will be supported by the carrier NTT DoCoMo in Japan, where the variant sold there will be known as the SC-04D within the docomo NEXT series of smartphone devices.
In Korea, two carriers support Galaxy Nexus; SK Telecom and KT, where the code of the phone is SHW-M420S and M420K respectively. The product name of Korean version of Galaxy nexus is yakjukr, which is not updated directly by Google. This variation of Galaxy Nexus shares the same hardware as GSM/HSPA+ version, making it one of the last non-LTE phones released in Korea. Both carriers provide 1,850mAh battery in comparison to 1,750mAh of all GSM releases of other countries, with 2,100mAh battery also provided free of charge.
In India, the Galaxy Nexus was initially supposed to launch in December 2011.Galaxy Nexus to hit Indian market this year not next | News | IT PRO India. Itpro.in (2011-11-07). Retrieved on 2011-11-21.Makwana, Samir. (2011-11-08) Galaxy Nexus to arrive in India by Mid-December. Themobileindian.com. Retrieved on 2011-11-21.Galaxy Nexus to Hit India by Mid-December. Siliconindia.com (2011-11-09). Retrieved on 2011-11-21. This was then rescheduled to the last week of January 2012.[tpl]cite web|author=Samsung IndiaSamsung_India |url=http://www.gsmarena.com/the_galaxy_nexus_launches_india_in_the_last_week_of_january-news-3531.php |title=The Galaxy Nexus launches in India in the last week of January - GSMArena.com news |publisher=Gsmarena.com |date= |accessdate=2012-02-20[/tpl] It was later rescheduled to March 2012 according to the official account of Samsung India on Twitter.[tpl]cite web|url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/technology/PersonalTech-Updates/Indian-launch-of-Galaxy-Nexus-delayed-to-March/SP-Article1-801413.aspx |title=Indian launch of Galaxy Nexus delayed to March |publisher=Hindustan Times |date=2012-01-24 |accessdate=2012-02-20[/tpl] but the phone failed to launch in March as per the statement. On May 3, 2012, Samsung India officially tweeted that "The Galaxy Nexus will not be launched in India. Watch this space for the next big thing!" confirming that the Galaxy Nexus will not see an India release.http://telecomtalk.info/samsung-galaxy-nexus-wont-coming-india-anymore/93118/#more-93118
In Hong Kong, the phone was available from December 15, 2011. It is available unlocked through local electronics stores (Broadway, Fortress, Suning, and others), and mobile phone operators (3, China Mobile, PCCW Mobile, one2Free, Smartone)
In Australia, Vodafone Australia announced that they would carry the Galaxy Nexus. It is available on Vodafone as well as Virgin Mobile.
In Thailand, the Galaxy Nexus was announced on December 14, 2011 and available for pre-order at the event. The pre-ordered devices shipped on December 22, 2011, the same day the phone was released.
In Singapore, the Galaxy Nexus was released on Saturday 11 February 2012, not exclusive to any carrier. It was also the first country to sell the white version, as a gift to those who waited due to its delay[tpl]cite web|url=http://www.facebook.com/SamsungMobieSingapore |title=Galaxy Nexus Released in White early as a surprise to those whowere waiting too ling  |publisher=Samsung Mobile Singapore |date=2012-02-11 |accessdate=2012-02-11[/tpl] (it was meant to arrive in January).
In Malaysia, it was released on January 16, 2012 by DiGi and Celcom.
In Indonesia, it was released on January 21, 2012.[tpl]cite web|url=http://www.samsung.com/id/galaxynexuslaunch/ Launch in Indonesia|title=Launch in Indonesia |date= |accessdate=2012-01-21[/tpl]
In Bahrain, Batelco launched the Galaxy Nexus on March 4, 2012.http://www.tradearabia.com/news/IT_213566.html
In Saudi Arabia, STC announced that it will solely introduce the Nexus. However, it was released on March 28, 2012.
On April 25, Google has completed supporting Arabic for ICS starting with 4.0.2, more of them updates are coming.

==Variants==

The device originally comes available in a black color. A white color version (with the front-panel in black[tpl]cite web|url=http://www.gsmarena.com/white_samsung_galaxy_nexus_images_surface_not_as_white_as_expected-news-3627.php |title=White Galaxy Nexus image surfaces, not as white as expected - GSMArena.com news |publisher=Gsmarena.com |date= |accessdate=2012-01-07[/tpl]) is expected to be available in February 2012.[tpl]cite web|last=Pierce |first=David |url=http://www.theverge.com/2012/1/5/2684475/white-galaxy-nexus-uk-price-release-date-handtec |title=White Galaxy Nexus coming to UK February 6th from Handtec |publisher=The Verge |date= |accessdate=2012-01-07[/tpl][tpl]cite web|url=http://www.engadget.com/2012/01/06/white-gsm-samsung-galaxy-nexus/ |title=White Galaxy Nexus to strut its stuff in UK on February 6th |publisher=Engadget |date= |accessdate=2012-01-07[/tpl][tpl]cite web|url=http://androidcommunity.com/white-galaxy-nexus-press-photos-appear-20120106/ |title=White Galaxy Nexus press photos appear |publisher=Android Community |date= |accessdate=2012-01-07[/tpl] There was a special edition released to Google employees with Google product logos on the back.http://thenextweb.com/google/2011/12/19/google-gives-out-customised-galaxy-nexus-handsets-to-employees-for-christmas/http://www.theverge.com/2011/12/19/2646072/google-hands-out-special-edition-galaxy-nexus-phones-to-employees

==Accessories==

The official Samsung accessory range includes a Desktop Dock with an HDMI port, a Desk Stand with a 3.5mm jack, a stand with a charging port for a second battery and a car holder that will let users turn their Galaxy Nexus phone into a SatNav replacement. There is also an official Samsung Galaxy Nexus battery that has recently become available in the UK.[tpl]cite news|url=http://www.mobi-city.co.uk/samsung-google-galaxy-nexus-1.html|title=MobiCity UK|publisher=MobiCity UK[/tpl] All of the Samsung accessories feature a microUSB port so the phone can be charged while it is being used.[tpl]cite web|url=http://www.samsung.com/us/mobile/cell-phones/SCH-I515MSAVZW-accessories |title=Accessories - Verizon Wireless Cell Phones SCH-I515 | Samsung Cell Phones |publisher=Samsung.com |date= |accessdate=2012-01-07[/tpl][tpl]cite web|url=http://www.gsmarena.com/official_samsung_galaxy_nexus_accessories_go_on_preorder_cost_dearly-news-3541.php |title=Official Samsung Galaxy Nexus accessories go on preorder - GSMArena.com news |publisher=Gsmarena.com |date= |accessdate=2012-01-07[/tpl] There are also several third-party accessories, including several protective cases,[tpl]cite web|last=Smith |first=Josh |url=http://www.gottabemobile.com/2011/12/19/galaxy-nexus-cases/ |title=15 Great Galaxy Nexus Cases |publisher=Gottabemobile.com |date=2011-12-19 |accessdate=2012-01-07[/tpl] batteries with more capacity,[tpl]cite web|url=http://www.androidcentral.com/new-store-seidio-innocell-3800mah-super-extended-battery-verizon-galaxy-nexus |title=New in the store: Seidio Innocell 3800mAh Super Extended Battery for Verizon Galaxy Nexus |publisher=Android Central |date= |accessdate=2012-02-20[/tpl] the Kogeto Dot 360-degree panoramic video accessory[tpl]cite web|last=Byford |first=Sam |url=http://www.theverge.com/2012/1/6/2687245/kogeto-iconic-panoramic-lens-galaxy-nexus |title=Kogeto iCONIC panoramic video coming to Galaxy Nexus and more |publisher=The Verge |date=2011-12-21 |accessdate=2012-01-07[/tpl][tpl]cite web|url=http://androidcommunity.com/kogeto-iconic-360-degree-panoramic-lens-announced-for-the-galaxy-nexus-20120106/ |title=Kogeto iCONIC 360-degree panoramic lens announced for the Galaxy Nexus |publisher=Android Community |date= |accessdate=2012-01-07[/tpl][tpl]cite web|url=http://www.engadget.com/2012/01/06/kogetos-iconic-for-android-brings-panoramic-video-to-the-masses/ |title=Kogeto's iCONIC for Android brings panoramic video to the masses |publisher=Engadget |date= |accessdate=2012-01-07[/tpl] and many others.[tpl]cite web|url=http://blog.fommy.com/news/19344/top-5-accessories-for-the-samsung-galaxy-nexus/ |title=Top 5 Accessories For The Samsung Galaxy Nexus | Fommy - Wireless Tech News and Reviews |publisher=Blog.fommy.com |date=2011-12-30 |accessdate=2012-01-07[/tpl][tpl]cite web|url=http://www.amazon.co.uk/tag/samsung%20galaxy%20nexus%20accessories/products |title=Products tagged with samsung galaxy nexus accessories |publisher=Amazon.co.uk |date= |accessdate=2012-02-20[/tpl][tpl]cite web|url=http://mobileaccessories.bestbuy.com/samsung-galaxy-nexus-accessories.htm |title=Samsung Galaxy Nexus Accessories (Cases, Chargers & Cables, Headsets, Screen Protectors, and more) - Best Buy Mobile Accessories |publisher=Mobileaccessories.bestbuy.com |date= |accessdate=2012-02-20[/tpl][tpl]cite web|url=http://www.paranoidandroids.com/samsung-galaxy-nexus-accessories.htm |title=Samsung Galaxy Nexus Accessories (Cases, Chargers & Cables, Headsets, Screen Protectors, and more) |publisher=Paranoid Androids |date= |accessdate=2012-02-20[/tpl]Samsung Galaxy Nexus AccessoriesSamsung Galaxy Nexus Accessories: Cases, Docks, Batteries, Screen Protectors and More

== Reception ==

The Galaxy Nexus generated a high level of anticipation[tpl]cite web|last=Webster |first=Scott |url=http://reviews.cnet.com/8301-19736_7-20116674-251/leaked-galaxy-nexus-details-point-to-verizon-exclusivity/ |title=Leaked Galaxy Nexus details point to Verizon exclusivity | Android Atlas – CNET Reviews |publisher=Reviews.cnet.com |date=2011-10-06 |accessdate=2011-10-30[/tpl][tpl]cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/business/ice-cream-sandwich-debuted-with-samsung-galaxy-nexus/2011/10/19/gIQALxeM0L_story.html |title=Ice Cream Sandwich debuted with Samsung Galaxy Nexus |publisher=The Washington Post |date= 2011-10-20|accessdate=2011-10-30 |first=Michelle |last=Singletary[/tpl][tpl]cite web|url=http://gizmodo.com/5850411/rumor-galaxy-nexus-coming-to-verizon-november-10th-for-an-ouchie-300 |title=Rumor: Galaxy Nexus Coming to Verizon November 10th for an Ouchie  |publisher=Gizmodo.com |date= |accessdate=2011-10-30[/tpl][tpl]cite web |url=http://newyork.ibtimes.com/articles/232581/20111017/galaxy-nexus-prime-ice-cream-sandwich-android.htm |title=Galaxy Nexus Prime & Ice Cream Sandwich Release, Price Leaked (video) |work=International Business Times |publisher=Newyork.ibtimes.com |date=2011-10-17 |accessdate=2011-10-30[/tpl][tpl]cite news |url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/technology/2011/10/galaxy-nexus-release-uk.html |title=Galaxy Nexus releasing November 17 – in the U.K. |last=Olivarez-Giles |first=Nathan |work=Los Angeles Times |date=October 28, 2011 |publisher=Latimesblogs.latimes.com |accessdate=2011-10-30[/tpl][tpl]cite web|last=Zeman |first=Eric |url=http://www.informationweek.com/news/personal-tech/smart-phones/231900194 |title=Samsung Galaxy Nexus: High-End Specs – Personal-tech – Smart Phones |publisher=Informationweek |date=2011-10-06 |accessdate=2011-10-30[/tpl] and was even regarded as the most anticipated Android device of 2011,The Samsung Galaxy Nexus and the launch that could have been. Android and Me. Retrieved on 2011-11-21.Galaxy Nexus Review 